OL,3,CSir Alister Jack given seat in House
OL,4,Cof Lords
OL,6,FThe former MP for Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway, Sir Alister Jack, has been
OL,8,Fgiven a seat in the House of Lords.
OL,10,FThe former Scottish Secretary was
OL,11,Fnominated by Rishi Sunak in the former
OL,12,FPrime Minister's resignation honours
OL,13,Flist.
OL,15,FHe has been awarded a peerage
OL,16,Falongside former cabinet colleagues
OL,17,Fincluding Michael Gove.
