OL,6,FSir Alister was the Conservative MP
OL,7,Ffor Dumfries and Galloway from 2017
OL,8,Funtil he stood down at the general
OL,9,Felection last summer.
OL,11,FHe served as Scottish Secretary
OL,12,Fbetween 2019 and 2024.JSir Alister
OL,13,FJack said: "I am deeply honoured to be
OL,14,Fappointed to the House of Lords.
OL,16,F"Serving the people of Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway in Westminster for seven
OL,18,Fyears and holding the role of
OL,19,FSecretary of State for Scotland for
OL,20,Ffive was a tremendous privilege.
