OL,3,CSir Alister Jack given seat in House
OL,4,Cof Lords
OL,6,F"When I stepped down as an MP at last
OL,7,Fyear's General Election, I was looking
OL,8,Fforward to new challenges. This
OL,9,Fopportunity was unexpected, but I
OL,10,Fwelcome the chance to use this
OL,11,Fplatform to speak up on issues I am
OL,12,Fpassionate about.
OL,14,F"Whether championing our rural economy
OL,15,For standing up for Scotland's vital
OL,16,Frole at the heart of the United
OL,17,FKingdom, I will remain a strong voice
OL,18,Ffor Scotland's interests in the House
OL,19,Fof Lords."
