OL,6,FHis citation from Mr Sunak says he:
OL,7,F"worked to ensure that devolution
OL,8,Fworked better for the people of
OL,9,FScotland and the United Kingdom.
OL,11,F"He oversaw multiple city deals
OL,12,Fbetween Scottish cities and the UK and
OL,13,FScottish governments as well as the
OL,14,Fcreation of two freeports in Scotland.
OL,15,FHe was the first Secretary of State to
OL,16,Fissue a Section 35 order, in response
OL,17,Fto the Gender Recognition Reform Bill.
OL,18,FThis constitutionally significant
OL,19,Fdecision was upheld by the Supreme
OL,20,FCourt."
