OL,6,FSNP deputy leader Pete Wishart said:
OL,7,F"While Alister Jack and Michael Gove
OL,8,Fsettle into their cushy "jobs" for
OL,9,Flife safe, unaccountable to voters,
OL,10,Fpeople across Scotland are still
OL,11,Fsuffering the effects of fourteen
OL,12,Fyears of Tory rule."
